Patient: What kind of food should I be eating?

Healthcare Educator: Eat lots of fruits, vegetables, and lean proteins. Try to avoid salty and fatty foods.

Patient: But I love my traditional foods. How can I give them up?

Healthcare Educator: You don't have to give them up. Let's find healthier versions of your favorite dishes.

Patient: How can I get fresh food if I'm scared to go outside?

Healthcare Educator: You can order your groceries online. They will deliver them to your doorstep.

Patient: I'm not good with computers. How can I do that?

Healthcare Educator: We can help you learn, or a family member could assist you with ordering online.